### Variables (replace with real IDs after seeding – get eventId and seatIds from GET events/:id/seats)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@eventId = {{eventId}}
@seatIds = {{seatIds}}
@reservationId = {{reservationId}}

### ========== RESERVATIONS ==========

### Lock seats (creates pending reservation – use eventId and available seat IDs from GET events/:id/seats)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/lock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "seatIds": ["{{seatIds}}"]
}

### Get my reservations
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/my-reservations

### Get reservation by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}

### Confirm reservation (after payment – use reservation ID from lock response)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/confirm

### Cancel reservation (only PENDING)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/cancel

